they were going to launch,

00:14:15.350 --> 00:14:16.752
CastleStorm-Free to Siege.

00:14:16.752 --> 00:14:18.210
And if you're a
game developer, you

00:14:18.210 --> 00:14:20.970
know that with every new title
you put so much work into it,

00:14:20.970 --> 00:14:23.950
and you want it to be
perfect when you launch it.

00:14:23.950 --> 00:14:26.000
So how do you do this?

