00:14:36.060 --> 00:14:37.530
So they posted it
on their website.

00:14:37.530 --> 00:14:39.490
They posted it on social media.

00:14:39.490 --> 00:14:41.410
Three days later,
they had 3,000 users

00:14:41.410 --> 00:14:43.770
