They said that the controls in a
couple places were hard to use.

00:14:59.750 --> 00:15:02.050
They mentioned exactly
where they were frustrated,

00:15:02.050 --> 00:15:03.860
and this allowed
ZenStudios to be

00:15:03.860 --> 00:15:07.180
able to improve user retention
at some tricky points.

00:15:07.180 --> 00:15:09.630
The other feedback
they got was-- well,

00:15:09.630 --> 00:15:11.950
different sorts of users
and different countries

00:15:11.950 --> 00:15:14.730
than they had expected actually
wanted to play their game.

00:15:14.730 --> 00:15:16.800
So they actually ended
up modifying their launch

00:15:16.800 --> 00:15:17.530
countries.

00:15:17.530 --> 00:15:20.140
