00:15:47.950 --> 00:15:50.660
So the result was they had
a really successful launch.

00:15:50.660 --> 00:15:52.966
They got a star
rating of 4.5 stars.

00:15:52.966 --> 00:15:54.590
And they now have
hundreds of thousands

00:15:54.590 --> 00:15:56.006
of happy users
playing their game.

