And it also can
allow you to see how

00:19:03.700 --> 00:19:06.100
users behave as they move
from your mobile apps

00:19:06.100 --> 00:19:09.650
across different
platforms to the web.

00:19:09.650 --> 00:19:13.260
So one of the best things
about Google Analytics,

00:19:13.260 --> 00:19:14.800
why it's so easy
to integrate, is

00:19:14.800 --> 00:19:16.950
it uses the Google
Play Services which

00:19:16.950 --> 00:19:19.370
is already on the user's device.

00:19:19.370 --> 00:19:22.020
This just means that you need
only a couple of lines of code

00:19:22.020 --> 00:19:25.470
